20// This reducer is part of the JavaScript pipeline and contains lowering of
21// wasm nodes (from inlined wasm functions).
22//
23// The reducer replaces all TrapIf / TrapUnless nodes with a conditional goto to
24// deferred code containing a call to the trap builtin.
25class WasmJSLowering final : public AdvancedReducer {
26 public:
27 WasmJSLowering(Editor* editor, MachineGraph* mcgraph,
28 SourcePositionTable* source_position_table);
29
30 const char* reducer_name() const override { return "WasmJSLowering"; }
31 Reduction Reduce(Node* node) final;
32
33 private:
34 WasmGraphAssembler gasm_;
35 const MachineGraph* mcgraph_;
36 SourcePositionTable* source_position_table_;
37};
38
39} // namespace v8::internal::compiler
